                              High cases with low coverage

             Business question
Which countries have high cancer cases but low prevention coverage? (CRITICAL) 

             Query
SELECT
	country_name,
	MAX(possible_cancer_cases)high_cases,
	MIN(coverage)low_coverage
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name;

Insight
Some countries have many cancer cases but poor healthcare coverage  and this is very dangerous.

Recommendation
These countries should be top priority for intervention
